The Software is the Community Edition of EzCoworker. A separate Enterprise
Edition is available from the Licensor and includes additional capabilities
including but not limited to: CEO Command Center, KPI Dashboards, IDE
Integration, Knowledge Graph Server, Database Semantic Layer, Data Intelligence
Agents, Code Migration Agents, Code Review Agents, Design Generation Agents,
Code Generation Agents, Test Automation Agents, Channel Integrations, and
advanced multi-agent orchestration.

Use of the Enterprise Edition is governed by a separate commercial agreement.
To enquire about Enterprise licensing, contact: hello@ezinsights.ai

